{"tid":1698583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共封殺電子煙保獨市生意","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T06:00:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebca3a8946ed39dab57b02608e5ce0a2bc155662","tid":1698583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191107/WKHCQQQIH2IROVD6UPZCRS6SV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191107%2FWKHCQQQIH2IROVD6UPZCRS6SV4%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9a4e0d74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191107%2FWKHCQQQIH2IROVD6UPZCRS6SV4%2F&h=1ec3bb35\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191107/WKHCQQQIH2IROVD6UPZCRS6SV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共封殺電子煙保獨市生意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191107/large/1573056979_d904.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573056979_d904.gif&h=bf7be0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電子煙受內地年輕人歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】雙11臨近，中國國家煙草專賣局聯合中國國家市場監督管理總局日前發通告稱，為保護未成年人的健康，「敦促電商平台及時關閉電子煙店舖」。內地最受歡迎的七個電子煙品牌集體跪低，支持當局的決定，京東商城則已將電子煙下架，而淘寶及天貓仍然有售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淘寶天貓仍有售<br />\n<br />\n早在2018年8月，內地已禁止向未成年人出售電子煙。當局今年雙11前再發通告敦促電子煙生產、銷售企業、電商平台，停止電子煙的互聯網銷售及廣告。分析指，年輕人群更青睞時尚、具個性的電子煙，以免做獨市生意的中國煙草總公司流失「下一代煙民」，因此中國國家煙草專賣局時隔一年，於本月1日再次強化此前的電子煙禁令。<br />\n<br />\n有關通告發佈幾個小時後，三個網絡平台已刪除電子煙產品；內地最受歡迎的七個電子煙品牌亦於同日晚上發聲明，稱支持監管機構決定。部份電子煙企業現已經在自家網站撤銷了電子煙產品銷售鏈接，京東商城、唯品會等10多間電商平台下架全部電子煙產品。然而《蘋果》發現，內地最大的電商平台&mdash;淘寶，仍未將電子煙下架。"},{"pid":"55920f4e4dbb6cafd283cf75a457fd118429e399","tid":1698583,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要 Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（求手動置頂）英國戰線Twitter要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8e5550cba8a3287387dc945b4e5d455240cc178","tid":1698583,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"利害了你的支 為了支那幼崽的健康 還是食真煙吧 遲D仲可能有鴉片 畢竟歷史循環"},{"pid":"82305a9141ea0ffb44b9c2ca8d1f7a82affad8f0","tid":1698583,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"香港咪一樣"},{"pid":"c8ea3e54dcca6947045ea8dc70b6f6331a467f44","tid":1698583,"uid":229920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82305a9141ea0ffb44b9c2ca8d1f7a82affad8f0","tid":1698583,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"香港咪一樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n日日妖魔化電子煙<br />\n唔通真煙就好健康"},{"pid":"edbd6b93b95f9a93ad5eb9b87b790e6385774836","tid":1698583,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"煙草稅 佔唔少政府收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電子煙搞串個party 財團梗唔like"},{"pid":"e67b4c8b22adf993952ee79db85d5e36f4d69712","tid":1698583,"uid":128923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8ea3e54dcca6947045ea8dc70b6f6331a467f44","tid":1698583,"uid":229920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82305a9141ea0ffb44b9c2ca8d1f7a82affad8f0","tid":1698583,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"香港咪一樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n日日妖魔化電子煙<br />\n唔通真煙就好健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"陳肇始本來就想用送中方法 夠票硬過 迫自由黨歸邊含撚<br />\n最後六月個時連自由黨同工聯會都反鳩佢檯 （因為呢d 唔係中聯辦硬任務）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.g